-> symbolic permmision

   symbol       type
     -        regular file
     d           directory
      1           symbolic link
       


     symbol        permmision
       r             read
       w             write
       x              execute
   
      permission                 file -                 directory d
        read r          allows a file to be read        allows file name in directory 
        write w         allows a file to be modified   allows entries to be modified in directory 
       execute x        allows to exevute a file        allows to access the content  and meta                                                    meta data  for entries  


     symbol            category
       u                  user
       g                  group
       o                  other
       a                  all
         
     -rw-r--r--    --> SECRET DECODER RING 
                              
   to change permission -> " chmod " change mode command
                              u g o a --> vcategory 
                               +      --> add permission
                               -      -->  remm=ove permmison 
                               =      -- set permmision 
                              rwx     -->  read write and execute
                              a = r   --> would change all the categorys permission to just r 
                               u=,    --> empty permmission removes all user will be ---
                               
                                 
